[[File:Star_Wars_RPG_Armored_Flight_Suit.jpg|thumb|An armored flight suit]]
The '''armored flight suit''' was a combat-ready light armor employed by space-faring types ranging from pilots to pirates and mercenaries. The suit provided protection against the vacuum of space for a limited time and came in various models including the [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] [[TX-3 combat flight suit/Legends|TX-3]] and [[TIE pilot#Uniform and equipment|Imperial TIE Suit]]. The armor cost 4,000 credits and weighed roughly 20 kilograms.

